# Frontend build-time env — FRAMEWORK-OWNED REFERENCE, adapted for catalyst
# (project ADR-0001/0002). Copy to `.env` (gitignored). Vite inlines VITE_* vars into
# the PUBLIC bundle at build time, so everything here is NON-SECRET config — NEVER put a
# secret in a VITE_ var. catalyst is public/auth-less: there is NO OIDC/MSAL config.

# Serverless-function API base (prod: the browser-visible base, origin + /api). Unset in
# dev → the api client falls back to "/api" (the Vite proxy → local `vercel dev`).
# VITE_API_URL=https://matthias-feyll.de/api
